name: Out of Fuel (KanielDing)
description:
Out of Fuel is a 2D physics based space puzzle game.

It's my 3-day submission for the MashUp Game Jam 2020!

PRESS M TO RETURN TO MENU AT ANY TIME!

This is my first ever game jam submission, so please leave any feedback you may have, good or bad, in the comments below! Thanks for playing :)
